  "title": "填鸭与速忘",
  "image_width": 847,
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"rvOPUqgS\"><b>填鸭与速忘</b>（Cram and dump）是一个贬义词，指的是学校里采用的陈腐学习规则：（1）在考试前（如果需要的话，在最后一晚）<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Cramming\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">死记硬背</a><sup data-text=\"死记硬背（填鸭式学习）\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/360416156\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>，（2）尽快忘记所有无用的知识。同样的贬义词还有<b>狂欢与宿醉</b>。</p><p data-pid=\"xCpiSRBb\">全世界的学生都这么干，因为考试要求的知识量太大，而且学生<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Kevin_Kruse%3A_School_serves_mindless_cramming\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">极不理解</a>知识对自己生活的重要性以及两者的关联。</p><p data-pid=\"YlFKHsxO\"><b>填鸭与速忘</b>和基于<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Self-directed_learning\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">学习内驱力</a><sup data-text=\"学习内驱力\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/52990549\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup>和<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Pleasure_of_learning\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">学习的乐趣</a><sup data-text=\"学习的乐趣\" data-url=\"https://www.zhihu.com/answer/1578551193\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"3\">[3]</sup>的有效的<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Self-directed_learning\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">自我导向学习</a><sup data-text=\"自我导向/自定进度/自学\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/353404375\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"4\">[4]</sup>相反。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"DZnFCYfl\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>题图 by betockIwm<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Cram_and_dump\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Cram and dump - supermemo.guru</a></blockquote>",
